# Lab 02 – Phân tích yêu cầu & Thiết kế Use Case

## Mini Project: Hệ thống quản lý đặt phòng khách sạn

### 1. Use Case Diagram (PlantUML)
```plantuml
@startuml
title Use Case Diagram – Hotel Booking Management System

left to right direction
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam usecase {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

actor Guest
actor "Receptionist/Admin" as Admin
actor "Payment Gateway" as PG
actor "Email Service" as ES

rectangle "Hotel Booking System" {
  (Search & View Rooms) as UC_Search
  (Register / Login) as UC_Login
  (Book Room) as UC_Book
  (Process Payment) as UC_Pay
  (Cancel Booking) as UC_Cancel
  (Manage Booking) as UC_Manage
  (Check-in / Check-out) as UC_Check
  (Manage Rooms & Prices) as UC_Rooms
  (Send Email Notifications) as UC_Notify
}

Guest -- UC_Search
Guest -- UC_Login
Guest -- UC_Book
Guest -- UC_Cancel

Admin -- UC_Manage
Admin -- UC_Check
Admin -- UC_Rooms

PG -- UC_Pay
ES -- UC_Notify

UC_Book ..> UC_Pay : <<include>>
UC_Manage ..> UC_Notify : <<include>>
UC_Cancel ..> UC_Notify : <<include>>
@enduml

